======================================================================

✅ GD_Primary_BBJ: eQTL and GWAS share a SINGLE causal variant (PP.H4 = 0.951).
   This overcomes the single-IV limitation of Wald ratio MR.

⚠️  GD_Repl_UKB: Evidence for DIFFERENT causal variants (PP.H3 = 0.774).
   MR signal may reflect locus-specific pleiotropy, not direct causality.

